column5: Hello, Does anyone have experience with this outfitter? They have lots of openings (at least for one camp) this summer, which seems odd this late in the game. Thank you.

Lady Google is your friend. Embrace her. Read about the hordes of zombie mice in cabins. Learn about the dam near fatal propane leak in one of the cabins. Even worse, educate yourself on the final fatal fly-in of a pilot attempting to land in a 50 knot wind.
